===Etymology===
{{ME.}} ''[[#Middle English|how]]'', ''[[hou]]'', ''[[hu]]'', ''[[hwu]]'', {{OE.}} ''[[hū]]'', from the same root as ''[[hwæt]]'', "who", "what"; akin to Old Saxon ''[[hww]]'', Dutch ''[[hoe]]'', compare German ''[[wie]]'' "how". See ''[[who]]'' and compare ''[[why]]''.

